<paragraph blockId="17.[189,1399,738,870]" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">
<bibRefCitation author="Chassagnard M. - T. &amp; Tsacas L. &amp; Lachaise D." box="[189,494,738,764]" journalOrPublisher="Annals of the Natal Museum" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" pagination="61 - 131" part="38" refId="ref12068" refString="Chassagnard M. - T., Tsacas L. &amp; Lachaise D. 1997. Drosophilidae (Diptera) of Malawi. Annals of the Natal Museum 38: 61 - 131." title="Drosophilidae (Diptera) of Malawi" type="journal article" year="1997">
Chassagnard 
<emphasis box="[347,407,738,764]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">et al.</emphasis>
(1997)
</bibRefCitation>
mentioned a species, named ‘ 
<taxonomicName authority="" authorityName="Sturtevant" authorityYear="1939" box="[851,1155,738,764]" class="Insecta" family="Drosophilidae" genus="Drosophila" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Sophophora">
<emphasis box="[851,984,738,764]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Drosophila</emphasis>
(
<emphasis box="[1002,1145,738,764]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Sophophora</emphasis>
)
</taxonomicName>
sp. C’, belonging to the ‘ 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Meijere" authorityYear="1916" box="[244,386,774,799]" class="Insecta" family="Drosophilidae" genus="Drosophila" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="montium">
<emphasis box="[244,386,774,799]" italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">D. montium</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species group’ in 
<collectingCountry box="[609,699,773,799]" name="Malawi" pageId="17" pageNumber="18">Malawi</collectingCountry>
with males having diffuse brown T2–T4 and pale T5 and T6. This species either belongs to one of the two species of this complex or represents a new species belonging to the complex. Elucidating its identity needs further investigation.
</paragraph>
